        Initializes the dynamic UI properties on a grid panel with two columns, label on the left, UI component on the right, and an optional help text below the UI component.
        Parameters:
        panelGrid - the panel grid instance to (re-)build.
        model - DynamicUiModel to extract properties from
        i18nPrefix - the name prefix for the I18N message resources.
        Throws:
        DynamicUiModelException - if the PSM could not be created by the dynamic UI model.
